RunPika
=======

It is a GNOME Shell Extension, where the speed of the Pikachu running in your taskbar indicates your CPU usage.

Installation
------------

* Link to shell extension --> https://extensions.gnome.org/extension/9833/runpika
* Requirements --> Linux + GNOME Desktop

More
----

* It is initially a derivative of RunCat by Sergei Kolesnikov.
* A rewrite of the original extension is in progress with additional features.
